      • getSourcedManagedObject

        default ManagedObject getSourcedManagedObject​(ManagedObject pooledManagedObject)
        Should the ManagedObjectPool create a wrapper ManagedObject for pooling, this method is required to be implemented to extract the ManagedObject sourced from the ManagedObjectSource.
        Parameters:
        pooledManagedObject - ManagedObject source from this ManagedObjectPool.
        Returns:
        ManagedObject sourced from the underlying ManagedObjectSource.
